Children's Privacy
Our services are not targeted for Individuals under the age of 13 or other ages who do not meet the criteria of an adult. If you are a child, before using our services, please obtain the consent from your guardian. We take children’s privacy seriously, if you are a child, please access our services under the supervision and guidance of parents or guardians.
Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Thus, you are advised to review this page periodically for any changes. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.